reviewText: Love love love this movie.  Great romance movie loaded with action.  Beautiful songs with a wonderful story line.  If you are looking for a good classic Indian movie, look no further.
Sharaabi is one of Amitabh Bachchan's greatest movies,I have it on dvd,A Must See for Amitabh Bachchan's Fans.. :)
This movie can be bought in most Indian stores that sell Dvds for less than $15.  Its a great movie, but i don't think anyone should pay this much for it.
Great movie, but $45? I got it for 12 and it came with another
